Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE WORLD SUMMIT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona is planning a world summit\Nto plan the battle with the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A world summit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gathering kings and leaders from\Nall over the world for a world meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona's planning that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Until now, leaders didn't work together,\Nsomething the Dark Army has exploited.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, Orzam, Ringaia,\Nand Carl have fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But, with the call of\Nthe young leader, Princess Leona,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the remaining leaders have decided to work\Nand plan together to face the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Leona meant by\Nsomething only she can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When and where will\Nthe world summit be held?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In a few days, at a location in Papunica.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I plan to depart tonight, but Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,would you like to join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, if important people\Nfrom all over will be there,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe someone will know\Nabout other legendary weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, we'll leave for Papunica\Nright away with Popp's Rura spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-In that case...\N-Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Without you,\Nwe would all have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a true Hero indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You showed me\Nthere's always a bigger fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll train to prepare for the upcoming\Nshowdown with the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?! After my\Namazing performance out there...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you! Why won't you praise me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Stop that!\N-Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough. You're making a fool of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you, you little ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you have the right\Nto talk down to me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell?\NThat's Grand Master Brokin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Eep!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This old man is the Grand Master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Brokin, the Holy Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Grand Master!\NWhy were you disguised?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I was curious to see\Nhow you two had improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are students of\NBrokin, the Holy Fist?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect all that to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but in the end, I got to see\Nthe results of Maam's training.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm gonna get chewed out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The experience was good for you,\Nwasn't it, Chiu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,For three years since I took you in,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason you never improved\Nwas because you always tried to show off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But that attack you used when you were\Ndesperate was quite impressive, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a proper hero, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got the biggest guts in Romos!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it is, Chiu.\NFame follows after.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't seek it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a pretty good master.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Master,\NI'd like to travel with Miss Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. If they give you permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, you three!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insist,\NI would be willing to help...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Rura.{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:06:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That was mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he hasn't learned\Nhis master's lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, he's an interesting guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at him,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,my worries about being human or not\Nseems almost insignificant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose we could use a guy like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Let me join your party!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban?! How did you find this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So your hideout was on this island\Nso close to the Field of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Hadorra?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera, let him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadorra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It matters not. I need to speak to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the man who failed at his\Nlast chance to kill Dai and was defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban, you're King Ban's\Nmost trusted vassal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you serve under me,\Nyet you wield more authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to inform King Ban\Nof my defeat, so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'm in no position to ask,\Nbut I must beg a favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,While I'm converted into a Superior Being,\Nwould you fight the humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The conversion is almost complete,\Nbut the humans are up to something big.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:08:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've learned leaders from around the world\Nare quietly gathering in Papunica.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to crush them for you?\NTo buy you time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Will that serve King Ban?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I know of Zamuza's defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Superior Beings are flawed creatures\Nthat can't cast spells after transforming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We have already found\Na solution to that flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic Power is lost in the process of\Nchanging from Darkling to Superior Being.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The solution to that is to turn this body\Ninto a Superior Being from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra, you would abandon\Nyour Darkling body?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You would live on as a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You would lose your immortality.\NWould you allow that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Disciples of Aban are enemies\Nworth that sacrifice. I now realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer want status or honor\Nor even this life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I must defeat them, even if it costs me\Nmy body, or my life will mean nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra, despite having\Nthe strongest body and abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason the Disciples of Aban\Ncontinued to beat you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,was your weakness of will\Nand your pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have cast those aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Having overcome your greatest weakness,\Nyou shall become the greatest warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban will be pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave Papunica to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Can he really be trusted?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice.\NI need time more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:10:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care who gives it,\Nso long as I can have one last chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. This is a pretty lovely country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, you're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the heck is this behemoth?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam! I heard you fought admirably!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your return is like\Ngiving a metal club to an ogre!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk about metal clubs\Nand ogres to a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my fellow student, Chiu.\NHe just joined us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this little rat\Nis up to being a party member?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:11:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he another male friend of Miss Maam's?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, Big Guy. He actually helped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miss Maam has pretty poor taste.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So where's the Princess and other leaders?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The world summit is being held... there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Papunica Grand Chapel.\NThey're gathered there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How surprisingly considerate of Myst\Nto show such leniency to Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But, if he's holding the Key of Ban,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it means King Ban\Nis allowing this attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:56.61,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}REFRACTOR FIST{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:01.61,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}TOMAKUGUTSOSHO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've gotten stronger.\NWe're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.51,0:12:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're impressive, too, Leona.\NTo unite leaders from around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, it's not all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We've heard nothing\Nfrom leaders of the fallen countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,At Ringaia, we only managed\Nto rescue General Bowson.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't find anyone in Orzam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And Queen Flora of\NCarl Kingdom is still missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. She's well known\Nfor being a bold, courageous woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I know she's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. More bold than the Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She could even be stronger than Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:13:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, does anyone in the world summit\Nknow about legendary swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask King Volken of Teran?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's known for his great knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A sword stronger than\Nthe Sword of Champions
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,likely doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The metal used in that sword,\NOrichalcum, was made my the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A small bit was given to humans\Nand made into legendary equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the Demon Dragon Blade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That sword was forged by the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a sword of the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any other powerful swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Summon Meruru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Meruru's in Papunica?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get to help Popp and the others already.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:14:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Dai, visualize the object you seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,When I tell you, drop that flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ra... n... ka... ku... su...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Rankakusu Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A small village that lies east\Nof Teran and Bengana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How will we get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.69,0:14:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe borrow Leona's Balloon Ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Or use Rura to somewhere close by?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We could use Rura to get straight there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, you've been to that village?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't go there. I left it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my place of birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your home village?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:15:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your family runs a weapon store, right?!\NThat might be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I ran away from home\Nto be Master Aban's student...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What a terrible landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me. I'm carrying a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,For making you come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We figured you being here would help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I want to help all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank goodness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's nothing like that fake one.\NShe's kind and warm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can see why Popp likes her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:16:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tiny village.\NNothing's changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The shop's up ahead. I'll be waiting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If Dad sees me, it'll be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that lady work in the weapon shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Popp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm sorry!\N-It's okay, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have really wanted to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, Popp is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:16:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You run off without a word\Nfor over a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can just waltz back\Nlike nothing's happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-You ungrateful son!\N-Honey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize we had customers.\NSorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe my idiot son\Nis actually helping the Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's helped us so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to Popp that we're even alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's our most reliable friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, mister, about what we said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. A legendary sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't find one in my shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But you might find something\Nat Ron's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a Darkling I met recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad! Is that Darkling's name, Ron Berku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. So?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard from Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The legendary craftsman who made his\NDark Armour Blade and Spear was named...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron Berku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if we ask him...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He lives in the forest like a hermit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't like meeting people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never put my heart into\Nmaking a weapon again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Much less a fool's errand like\Nthe world's greatest sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My interests lie solely in\Nhow the weapons I make perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But recently, there's been\Na lack of decent wielders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how powerful the weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,if the wielder is a dud,\Nthen it's nothing but an ornament.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Those swords over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I forged them for drinking money,\Nbut they're better than a normal sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:18:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Take one and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Better than normal isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.43,0:19:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even your Dark Armour Blade couldn't\Nendure my power and crumbled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Make a sword\Nstronger than that Dark Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I can't hope to beat\Nthe Demon Dragon Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Demon Dragon Blade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You fought that weapon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And?! What was the result?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I broke their sword,\Nbut mine disintegrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You broke it? You broke\Nthe Demon Dragon Blade with my sword?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful! That's magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ron, what's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I not be overjoyed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Demon Dragon Blade was forged\Nby the gods as the world's greatest sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the ultimate weapon\Nthat I spent over a century pursuing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To hear that the Dark Sword I forged\Nout of an inferior metal broke it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You've impressed me, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,With you as its wielder,\NI can forge the world's greatest sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If I make it out of the same material,\Nit will beat the Demon Dragon Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then please! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. I said, "the same material."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The same as the Demon Dragon Blade.\NOrichalcum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Find me some Orichalcum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no Metallurgist.\NWithout material, I can't forge a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. So we're back to square one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But we just need to find some Orichalcum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:20:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Easier said than...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Crown of Champions!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,King Romos said it's made of Orichalcum!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,To Dermline Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa! Where?! Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My Crown of Champions!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?! Oh! This!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops! That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's our Orichalcum!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-Bye, Grampa!\N-Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Rura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.90,0:21:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Clean up after yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you face the devil\NWith logic on your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:07.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatoe akuma ni seiron kazashite\Nmukatte mitemo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may just be a rationalization{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:11.35,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sore wa akumade seitouka\Nsashite chigai wa naikamo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, even now I waver{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:15.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo ima mo yureteiru kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far will we go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:19.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a voice like an angel's whisper{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.78,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tenshi no sasayaki nimo nita\Nkoe ga kikoeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an imposter's illusion\NIt still rang in my ears{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:26.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatamata petenshi no mayakashi\Nhitokiwa mimi ni hibiiteita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exposed to love and sorrow{\i0}
